- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques for detection in the audio sensing system. 
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems): The paper discusses energy-efficiency in IoT systems, which often involve embedded systems. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper presents a resource consumption model and discusses the trade-off between detection performance and energy consumption, which can be related to information theory. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses energy-efficiency in IoT systems, which involve networking and communication aspects.
